title: BRIEF-IDEX receives first production order for new off-chip touch sensor
text:
Sept 21 Idex ASA :
* Received first order for production quantities of its new off-chip sensor product from World Wide Touch Technology Holding Ltd (WWTT)
Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
